<div class="container-fluid SliderBg SliderBorder Divider InnerTitle">
    <div class="container Divider">
        <h1 class="">
            <span>Snow Schoolers is a new place to find affordable ski lessons from expert ski and snowboard instructors in the North Lake Tahoe area. </span>
        </h1>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
            <h2 class="BigHeader" style="margin-bottom:0">Fun and Affordable Lessons for All</h2>
            <hr>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="icon-star"></i> Planning your first ever trip to Tahoe?</br></br></li>
                <li><i class="icon-star"></i> Need to brush off some rust after years away from the slopes?</br></br></li>
                <li><i class="icon-star"></i> Or simply looking to elevate your skills to the next level?</li>
            </ul>

        </div>
        <div class="span6">
            <div class="carousel slide" id="myCarousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="item active">
                        <%= image_tag 'ski-large1.jpg' %>
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h3>It's a great day to take off work</h3>
                            <p>Sure beats the grind don't it?</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <%= image_tag 'ski-large2.jpg' %>
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h3>Action packed day for these two</h3>
                            <p>What's with the helicopter anyway?</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <%= image_tag 'ski-large3.jpg' %>
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h3>Well that looks intense</h3>
                            <p>Trees are no obstacle after training with us!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a data-slide="prev" href="#myCarousel" class="left carousel-control">‹</a>
                <a data-slide="next" href="#myCarousel" class="right carousel-control">›</a>
            </div>
            <p class="StyleP">From first-weekers to thrill-seekers our instructors will help you master any challenge!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="container Divider">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="span12">
                    <hr>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
